1.text: Mangwanani anhasi, mhepo yanga yava kumhanya makiromita 83 paawa uye yanga iri kuratidza kuti icharamba ichipera simba.

2.text: Mwoyo ndiwo nhengo yakakura yekufambiswa kwezvese mumuviri, zvakare ndiwo unopomba ropa.

3.text: Mawebhusaiti aya akawana kutariswa kwakawanda, zvikuru sei muchikamu chezvekudzidza.

4.text: Kushanya kunochipa kana vanhu vakashanya vari zvikwata, saka kana uri wega kana kuti uine shamwari imwe chete, edzai kubatana nevamwe vanhu moumba chikwata chevanhu vana kana vatanhatu kuti muderedze mutengo unobhadhara munhu mumwe chete.

5.text: Mamwe makamera emafirimu epakati anoshandisa fomati ye6 ne6 cm fomati, kunyanyisa negative 56 ne56 mm.

6.text: Gadzira uye utakure makopi egwaro rako uyezve famba nenhamba dzeavo vakakuitira inishuwarenzi.

7.text: Inwa kofi yakakora mangwanani uye inwa putugadzike yekuzorora yechamomile manheru.

8.text: Kuwondomoka kwechando hakuna kusiyana nezvinozivikanwa; materu akadzika anobata chando zvishoma, chinenge chasarira chose chinozodzika chichiwondomoka.

9.text: Mutero pamari yatambirwa yakagadzirwa zvakasiyana munyika dzakasiyana, uye zvikero nezvikamu zvinosiyana siyana zvakanyanya kubva kunyika imwe neimwe.
